days.text: Slight flooding will occur in Inner Harbour area from 8 pm ~ 0 am due to astronomical tide. Cloudy apart from sunny intervals. Light rain later. Force 3 to 4 northeasterly winds, becoming force 5 easterly winds with gusts.
Cloudy. Rain. Force 4 to 5 easterly winds, occasionally force 6 with gusts.
Cloudy, becoming fine. Force 3 to 5 easterly winds with gusts.
Fine apart from cloudy periods. Force 2 to 3 north to northeasterly winds.
Cloudy apart from sunny periods. Force 3 to 4 northerly winds.
